# Feature 011 — DQL Syntax Highlighting (best-effort GitHub viewing)
# DormantQL has no first-class GitHub Linguist support yet. Map .dql/.dqls to a close
# existing language so the repo's schema/operation files render with usable coloring on
# GitHub instead of plain text. This is a deliberate best-effort fallback; first-class
# highlighting via a Linguist Tree-sitter contribution remains planned follow-up work.
# Repo owners adopting DormantQL can copy these two lines into their own .gitattributes.
*.dql  linguist-language=TypeScript
*.dqls linguist-language=TypeScript
